span>（基本法50）<br />\n<br />\n（五）過半可以否決政府議案及財政預算案，但<span style=\"color: red;\">行政長官可以解散立法會重選</span>（基本法50）<br />\n<br />\n（六）四分一議員聯合動議可提彈劾案，成立調查委員會，要三分二議員通過，最後<span style=\"color: red;\">中央政府作最終決定</span>（基本法73）<br />\n<br />\n（七）人大可以對基本法釋法，或修改基本法（基本法158、159）<br />\n<br />\n結論：立法會沒有權拿到五大訴求的任何一項，過半的唯一作用是無限否決所有政府議案，達致攬炒，令社會無法運作<br />\n<br />\n#其實立法會係無立法權<br />\n#個啲叫否決權<br />\n#立法會101<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2020/03/09/204569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2020%2F03%2F09%2F204569&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XeliHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=cb8ebf3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2020/03/09/204569</a><br />\n<br />\n投唔投，投邊個，自己諗，但唔好幻想35+之後改變到d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"我就係想要個否決權，一開始提35+就係為呢樣野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講極都唔撚明"},{"pid":"1cf64dba054bb78ea88769caba866121f3a5365b","tid":2057944,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"做就照做<br />\n不過唔係淨係做呢樣<br />\n有好多野重要過35+<br />\n咁都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61126e6097fddeac15d4434cd581eacb5eeb588","tid":2057944,"uid":201004,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3a3f199eed6b1681fc1d3cb07cf2cb72f5478ee0","tid":2057944,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd12d127968bc2c4804fac48adb8766369999caa","tid":2057944,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"9c1d8da10573d43be4e5defdfd97173f3dfac17e","tid":2057944,"uid":264326,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"我就係想要個否決權，一開始提35+就係為呢樣野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci